{
  "stem": "10181.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I still can see her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In my mind, I can still see her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was very good with little kids.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She didn't teach us, but she was very good with little kids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in Westerbork, also, at one time or another, there were very famous people there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, the Dutch Jews were very integrated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "For instance, the orchestra, the concert orchestra, all the violinists, I think to the very last one, were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So at one time, they picked them all up and brought them to Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then the Germans asked them to give a concert for them, you know, so they gave a concert for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they probably thought that if they gave concerts for the Germans, they would be deferred.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, they were deferred for maybe a week or two.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And unfortunately, I think if I remember rightly reading afterwards the story of Westerbork, that I think one survived of the whole-- of this whole group of violinists.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then-- there was-- I don't remember his name-- there was a famous Jewish boxer who was well known, Dutch Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was bought into the camp, so he started organizing, like, exercising and-- and teaching young men if they want to box.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was to-- you know, so they used to have boxing exhibitions for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This-- this was a crazy situation when you think about it, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "This was a camp where-- where next week you might be dead, but the Germans came and watched you an exhibition of boxing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Or they had a concert, or they had plays.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You know, they-- they had plays.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "People were performing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They had people who were-- who were actors, and they performed and-- and-- and all these kind of things.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
